# Keep the root-context Docker build (docker/Dockerfile) sane. That build only needs
# Cargo.*/rustfmt.toml/crates for the Rust stage; everything listed here is multi-GB
# and irrelevant to it. Honored by both the classic and BuildKit builders.
# (Sub-context builds — docker/egress-proxy, context-engine, blog — are unaffected;
# their build context is their own directory, not the repo root.)
.git
target
repos
**/node_modules
blog/dist
